      "span_text": "FL5.12 cells stably expressing Bcl-x L together with either wild-type or mutant Bad (FL5.12-Bcl-x L -Bad cells; a gift of S. Korsmeyer) were cultured as described [CITATION_1] except that recombinant IL-3 (0.5 ng ml -1 ) was used instead of WEHI-cell-conditioned media."
